{"tid":1784932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 請各路人士馬上籌備星期六日和你shop","createTime":"2019-12-16T04:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T04:41:40.000Z","uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5706d13929ad026474b430450d4c64defd07d5b","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"星期六日呢啲日子和你shop極其有效打擊經濟<br />\n之前已經有人講過<br />\n如果班狗發癲 成個商場攬炒<br />\n如果班狗唔做嘢 美心 怡和嗰啲收定皮都得<br />\n但前提我地要人多 冇人乜都做唔到<br />\n而且我地要吹大個風先 誇張聲勢<br />\n即係新城市點都收得皮架啦<br />\n商家識做就自己評估定形勢 唔係後果自負<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且吹大個風係想有多啲人一齊嚟<br />\n話之你喺商場一齊唱聖誕歌<br />\n總之要多人<br />\n唔裝修淨係巡遊已經好好玩<br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢到可以參考啲公關技巧 抵讚架<br />\n教大家點樣喺和你Shop嘅時候做好公關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784551</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"339bbdd09dd1afccf86d57feb8ca0091c08486be","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"和你shop打擊經濟"},{"pid":"695493f34d5b56ffef50d0dd246cd81375a6acf4","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"和你shop打擊經濟"},{"pid":"d8e720c9212e61b827978da62e5906306e4f251f","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"和你shop打擊經濟"},{"pid":"57658f0e2ac37b346d6106521127587caed55a03","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"和你shop打擊經濟"},{"pid":"e13fc3a0bdddb976039d3eebe9a8ce558bed6a19","tid":1784932,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔識整文宣呀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc659e0917bf8a7da16b49e85debbc98718d13a","tid":1784932,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:33:13.000Z","ms